- cs.MM (Multimedia): The dataset and benchmark are related to multimedia data, specifically images of paintings. 
- cs.DL (Deep Learning): The paper mentions the use of deep learning approaches for painting restoration, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper deals with the restoration of graphical content, specifically paintings, which is relevant to this sub-category. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper may also be relevant to this sub-category as it involves the preservation of cultural heritage, which has implications for human-computer interaction and user experience.
